# Publisher Regression Guardrails

- Keep publisher fail-closed: ambiguous state must return error, not success.
- Success must require post-submit URL verification to non-write board list/view.
- Prefer scoped selectors that disambiguate duplicated buttons in draft list/modals.
- Keep waits bounded (`BOT_MAX_WAIT_MS`) and avoid unbounded retries.
- Preserve debug artifact capture for triage:
  - Step screenshots when `PUBLISHER_DEBUG_SCREENSHOTS=true`
  - Trace zip when `PUBLISHER_DEBUG_TRACE=true` (failures persist always; successes use `PUBLISHER_TRACE_SUCCESS_SAMPLE_PERCENT`)
  - `error.png` on publisher failure when page exists
- After publisher flow edits, run `npm run lint` and `npm run test:integration`.

